The paper discusses the evaluation of feature-based explainers for machine learning image classifiers, which falls under the domain of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a new metric for evaluating the quality of explainers, which is relevant to the field of machine learning (cs.LG) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper discusses the theoretical analysis of the proposed metric, which is relevant to the field of cryptography (cs.CR).
